    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It should be possible to have your own script that locates a notebook in package data, and launches the notebook server for it. To find the location, use:\n\n``` python\nimport mypackage\nmypackage.__file__\n```\n\nClosing as I don't think we're likely to do anything on this; and if we do the relevant repo is now jupyter/notebook.\n"
